snippet.title: Salt 2: Shores of Gold | Kickstarter Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
The Salt 2 Kickstarter is live! Support us here: https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/1392020915/salt-2-shores-of-gold

Salt 2: Shores of Gold is an open world pirate exploration and survival game set in an infinite procedural world. 

Wishlist on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1574900/Salt_2_Shores_of_Gold/?beta=0
Website: https://www.saltthegame.com/​
Discord: https://discord.gg/nCkcdkk​
Twitter: https://twitter.com/lavabootsstudio​
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/lavaboots/​
Reddit: https://www.reddit.com/r/ProjectSalt/
